high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter.
Bring the lettuce to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Bring the chilled lettuce to the sink.
Put the chilled lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce to the right of a loaf of bread.
Turn right and walk a few steps to the fridge then turn to face it.
Put the lettuce in the top portion of the fridge on the bottom shelf and close the door letting it cool off then retrieving it and closing the door again.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the head of lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold head of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the upper fridge doors, place the head  of lettuce inside, and close the doors, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the head of lettuce then close the doors.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the chilled head of lettuce in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the sink basin.
